{"word":"γεωμετρέω","slug":"γεωμετρέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>γεωμετρέω</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>from <a href='S:γεωμέτρης'><el>γεωμέτρης</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to measure the earth, to practise</i> or <i>profess geometry</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to measure</i>, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}